    UITree

    public abstract class AbstractTree
extends UIDataAdaptor
implements org.richfaces.component.MetaComponentResolver, org.richfaces.component.MetaComponentEncoder, org.richfaces.event.TreeSelectionChangeSource, org.richfaces.event.TreeToggleSource

    The <rich:tree> component provides a hierarchical tree control. Each <rich:tree> component typically consists of <rich:treeNode> child components. The appearance and behavior of the tree and its nodes can be fully customized.

    Author:
    Nick Belaevski
